7)  NPC's don't attack each other, instead when moving to occupied cell push
    monster in occupied cell out of the way
8)  When an entity tries to move to an occupied space (pc monster combat) happens
    a)  When attack happens the damage of the attack is calculated by rolling the ad dice
        and the result is subtracted from the defenders hp
    b)  when a character's hp goes below zero the character dies
9)  The game ends in a win if the PC kills a NPC with the BOSS flag, not when the dungeon
    is empty of NPC's